102
00:06:29,541 --> 00:06:32,581
Aku tak pernah
mendengar pahlawan sepertimu.

103
00:06:32,581 --> 00:06:34,581
Emang gua peduli?!

104
00:06:33,081 --> 00:06:34,241
Gua ini pemula!

105
00:06:34,421 --> 00:06:37,991
