Soalnya itu akan merusak
reputasi pahlawan lain.

108
00:06:44,561 --> 00:06:47,101
Hei, bukankah itu Tanktop Tiger?

109
00:06:47,101 --> 00:06:49,141
Benar, itu Tanktop Tiger.

110
00:06:49,141 --> 00:06:50,271
Benarkah?!

111
