00:07:00,961 --> 00:07:03,281
Jadi bagaimana, anak baru?

114
00:07:03,281 --> 00:07:07,121
Mau mengamuk di sini dan
membuatku terlihat keren?

115
00:07:07,121 --> 00:07:08,791
<i>Shuriken Meledak.</i>

116
00:07:11,011 --> 00:07:12,631
Shuriken Meledak

117
00:07:16,001 --> 00:07:17,501
Tanktop Tiger?!

118
00:07:17,501 --> 00:07:18,881
