121
00:07:25,371 --> 00:07:27,061
Hei, panggil pahlawan!

122
00:07:27,101 --> 00:07:29,101
Pahlawan!

123
00:07:28,101 --> 00:07:29,221
Lari!

124
00:07:30,161 --> 00:07:31,351
Saitama.

125
00:07:31,991 --> 00:07:36,021
Jadi kau menjadi salah
satu Pahlawan tak berguna itu?

126
00:07:37,331 --> 00:07:39,651
Kalau begitu, aku hanya perlu

127
00:07:39,651 --> 00:07:43,911
membuat situasi di mana kau tak bisa
menolak bertarung denganku, Pahlawan Saitama!

128
00:07:45,671 --> 00:07:47,241
<i>Hujan Pembantaian!</i>

129
00:07:57,391 --> 00:07:58,761
Hentikan, oi!

130
00:07:59,151 --> 00:08:01,841
Saitama, bertarunglah denganku!

131
00:08:01,901 --> 00:08:03,431
Kau seorang pahlawan, 'kan?

132
00:08:03,431 --> 00:08:04,891
Atau kubunuh mereka semua!

